      "body": "Nice explanation and introduction to flow fields. Meat and potatoes for hydrodynamicists.\n\nFun story from undergrad. A friend and I took intro to fluid dynamics before we took E&M. We walked into the E&M class and the prof started with electric fields. I leaned over and said: Hey, Drew! It's inviscid flows! \ud83d\ude09\n\nWound up in radiation hydrodynamics. That uses ALL the terms.\ud83d\ude31",
